 Z←JNUINV JDN;L;N;I;J;D;M;Y
⍝ Inverse of JNU: Julian day number → M D Y
⍝ Standard Meeus inverse algorithm
 L←⌊JDN+68569.5
 N←⌊4×L÷146097
 L←L-⌊((146097×N)+3)÷4
 I←⌊4000×(L+1)÷1461001
 L←31+L-⌊1461×I÷4
 J←⌊80×L÷2447
 D←L-⌊2447×J÷80
 L←⌊J÷11
 M←J+2-12×L
 Y←(100×N-49)+I+L
 Z←M D Y
⍝ Verify round-trip; adjust day if needed
 :If JDN≠JNU Z
   Z[2]←Z[2]+⌊0.5+JDN-JNU Z
 :EndIf
